@startmindmap
<style>
:depth(0) {
    BackgroundColor #FF5F46
    LineColor #FF5F46
    FontColor #ffffff
    LineThickness 3.0
}
:depth(1) {
    BackgroundColor #0078D4
    LineColor #0078D4
    LineThickness 3.0
    FontColor #FFFFFF
}
:depth(2) {
    BackgroundColor #ffb900
    LineColor #ffb900
    LineThickness 3.0
    FontColor #000000
}
boxless {
    FontColor #000000
}
</style>
+ Configure CDC\nFlows in SQL
++ SQL AUTO CDC Syntax
+++_ CREATE OR REFRESH STREAMING TABLE
+++_ CREATE FLOW ... AS AUTO CDC INTO
+++_ FROM stream(source_table)
++ Key Clauses
+++_ KEYS (columns): primary keys
+++_ APPLY AS DELETE WHEN: delete expression
+++_ SEQUENCE BY: ordering column
+++_ COLUMNS * EXCEPT (...): exclude columns
-- SCD Type 1 SQL
---_ STORED AS SCD TYPE 1
---_ Current state only
-- SCD Type 2 SQL
---_ STORED AS SCD TYPE 2
---_ TRACK HISTORY ON: selective tracking
---_ last_login changes → no new history row
@endmindmap
